    <item>
      <title>电动汽车巨头之争中比亚迪销量首次超越特斯拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/byd-sales-beat-tesla-for-first-time-in-battle-of-ev-giants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国比亚迪股份有限公司公布季度营收，自两家公司在全球电动汽车销量上展开激烈竞争以来，首次超过特斯拉公司。彭博电视台的 Minmin Low 报道了这一消息。（视频中删除了数据错误的图表）（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-31/byd-sales-beat-tesla-for-first-time-in-battle-of-ev-giants</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 00:17:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
